{"id":48,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":48,"title":"Chapter 45: Jesus Christ Teaches about the Sacrament and Prayer","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 45","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 45"],["h1","Jesus Christ Teaches about the Sacrament and Prayer"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_048_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p3"},"Jesus Christ sent his disciples to get some bread and wine. He told the Nephites to sit on the ground."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.1-2"},"3 Nephi 18:1–2"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_048_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p5"},"When the disciples returned, the Savior broke the bread into pieces and blessed it. He gave some to his disciples and had them give some to the people."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.3-4"},"3 Nephi 18:3–4"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_048_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p7"},"Jesus said that people who take the sacrament promise to always remember him and his sacrifice. They then receive his Spirit."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.7"},"3 Nephi 18:7"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_048_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p9"},"Jesus Christ blessed the wine and gave some to his disciples. The disciples gave some wine to the people."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.8"},"3 Nephi 18:8"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_048_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p11"},"Jesus said those who take the sacrament promise to keep his commandments."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.10"},"3 Nephi 18:10"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_048_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p13"},"Jesus again told his disciples that everyone who takes the sacrament and always remembers him will have his Spirit."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.11"},"3 Nephi 18:11"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_048_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p15"},"He told his disciples they would be blessed if they kept his commandments."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.14"},"3 Nephi 18:14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_048_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p17"},"He told them to pray always and to pray as they had seen him pray."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.15-16"},"3 Nephi 18:15–16"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_048_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p19"},"The Savior told all the Nephites to pray to Heavenly Father in his name. He also commanded them to pray with their families."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.19,21"},"3 Nephi 18:19, 21"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_048_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p21"},"He said the people should meet together often. They should welcome others to their meetings, pray for them, and be good examples to them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.22-24"},"3 Nephi 18:22–24"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_048_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p23"},"The Savior gave his disciples the power to give the Holy Ghost. Then a cloud covered the people so that only the disciples saw Jesus Christ go up to heaven."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-45-jesus-christ-teaches-about-the-sacrament-and-prayer.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.36-39"},"3 Nephi 18:36–39"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
